ZH: 我们需要适应新的工作环境。
EN: We need to adapt to the new working environment.

ZH: 这个孩子很快适应了新学校。
EN: The child adapted quickly to the new school.

ZH: 我们必须适应气候的变化。
EN: We must adapt to the changes in climate.

ZH: 我们要适应不同的文化背景。
EN: We need to adapt to different cultural backgrounds.

ZH: 她花了一些时间来适应新的生活方式。
EN: It took her some time to adapt to the new lifestyle.

ZH: 这项技术正在适应市场需求。
EN: This technology is adapting to market demands.

ZH: 为了适应这个城市的快节奏，我每天早上都去跑步。
EN: To adapt to the fast pace of this city, I go for a run every morning.

ZH: 当你去外地旅行，你需要适应当地的风俗习惯。
EN: When you travel abroad, you need to adapt to the local customs.

ZH: 虽然刚开始有困难，但是他很快适应了这份工作。
EN: Although he had difficulties at first, he quickly adapted to this job.

ZH: 适应新的时间区域需要一些调整。
EN: Adjustments are needed to adapt to a new time zone.

ZH: 为了适应这个变化，我们需要改变我们的策略。
EN: To adapt to this change, we need to change our strategy.

ZH: 这个电子产品设计得很人性化，适应不同年龄段的用户。
EN: This electronic product is designed to be user-friendly and adaptable to users of different age groups.

ZH: 他的心眼太小，无法适应新的挑战。
EN: He has a narrow mindset and cannot adapt to new challenges.

ZH: 适应环境变化是进步的关键。
EN: Adapting to environmental changes is the key to progress.

ZH: 她没有办法适应这种腐败的社会。
EN: She couldn't adapt to this corrupt society.

ZH: 在新的公司，迅速适应工作要求非常重要。
EN: In a new company, it is important to adapt quickly to job requirements.

ZH: 在异国他乡，要适应新的语言是挑战性的。
EN: It is challenging to adapt to a new language in a foreign land.

ZH: 只有适应变化，我们才能生存下去。
EN: Only by adapting to change can we survive.

ZH: 他勇敢地适应了一年的国外生活。
EN: He bravely adapted to a year of living abroad.

ZH: 学习一门新技能需要时间来适应和掌握。
EN: Learning a new skill takes time to adapt and master.
